data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious 2-story beauty boasts 4 generous bedrooms and 2.5 baths, making it perfect for your family. Say goodbye to carpet hassles – this home features easy-to-maintain flooring throughout. With a 2-car garage, a 1-year-old roof, and a breathtaking lake view, it's an ideal retreat.Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this gem offers both tranquility and convenience. Don't miss out – make this slice of paradise yours today!
